Case Study

Welcome:
Login/Register   |      Add/Remove Users from Database
User Profile Page           |    Edit/Customize
Products           |    Products/Descriptions/Prices
Favorites Page           |    View/Like/Unlike Products
Cart System               |    Add/Remove/Total
Admin Page               |    Add or Update Products

Tables
Users - many to many - Products
Order_products
Orders
user_roles
Products

Can have multiple orders from products
Multiple users can buy the same product
User Stories | As a user, I want to:

As a user, I want to be able to Create an account
As a user, I want to be able to Login to my account
As a user, I want to be able to Logout of my account
As a user, I want to be able to Buy products
As a user, I want to be able to Save favorites for easier checkout
As a user, I want to be able to View my cart and totals
As a user, I want to be able to Add items to my cart

Technologies and Skills
Html 5 | Bootstrap 5 | CSS 3 | JavaScript | Java | SpringBoot / Spring MVC|  JPA | Junit |



